6. **Test strategy** — what to test, at what level (unit / integration / e2e). Cite specific behaviors, not "test everything."
7. **Risks & mitigations** — what could go wrong and how the design handles it.
8. **Out of scope** — anything the PRD asked for that this design defers, with rationale.

